The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sport
		 Monday, July 28, 2003  IN THE CITY
				 																																																	 Bharat Petroleum beat Bata 1-0 in the Ibiza six-a-side corporate football tournament final on Sunday. Former international Amit Bhadra turned out for the champion team. Eighteen teams took part in the competition.				 																																																	 CCFC, the ILSS A and B teams and International Club reached the semi-finals of the third state inter-club darts championship. In the quarter finals, CCFC beat DKS 3-0, ILSS A defeated RCGC 3-0, ILSS B overcame Saturday Club 3-1, while International Club pipped CSC 3-0.				 																																																	FOOTBALL: Federation Cup: Haywards Sporting vs Mahindra United (3 pm), Air India vs Dempo SC (6 pm). Matches at Salt Lake Stadium.				 																																																	DARTS: Inter-club meet at International Club from 6.30 pm.				 																																																	TABLE TENNIS: Inauguration of all-India BSNL meet at SAI complex at 10.30 am.
